flowchart TD
    A[Git Push] --> B[GitHub Action<br/>doc-generator]
    B --> C[POST /api/repositories<br/>Authorization: Bearer repo token]

    C --> D[Nginx /api proxy]
    D --> E[Rust Server<br/>apps/server]

    E --> E1[Validate repository token]
    E1 --> E2[Upsert repository metadata in Postgres]
    E2 --> E3[Clone repository at exact commit SHA]
    E3 --> E4[Preprocess repository<br/>ignore patterns + max size]
    E4 --> E5[Generate repository tree]

    E5 --> F1[Send start email]
    E5 --> F2[POST /docs-gen to Wiki service]

    F2 --> G[Wiki API<br/>apps/wiki]
    G --> G1[Validate API key + payload]
    G1 --> G2[Run PlannerAgent<br/>wiki structure]
    G2 --> G3[Index repository chunks in Qdrant]
    G3 --> G4[For each section:<br/>retrieve context + run writer]
    G4 --> G5[Write markdown files:<br/>/wiki_output/{repo_id}/NN-section.md]

    G5 --> H[Return docs generation result]

    subgraph Infra
      I1[(Postgres)]
      I2[(Qdrant)]
      I3[Local LLM / Ollama-vLLM]
      I4[(Shared Volume<br/>wiki_output)]
    end

    E2 --> I1
    G3 --> I2
    G4 --> I2
    G2 --> I3
    G4 --> I3
    G5 --> I4
